{
  "stem": "27443.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They probably got certain orders from the German [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that certain people have to leave and certain people remain.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because after we left, there were-- they formed a larger ghetto, and people were confined in a certain part of the city, that they formed a Yiddish ghetto.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were not there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived to [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Krupp, ?] we were resettled again from the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were given-- as a family, we got an empty room in a certain part of town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time, it was formed that the whole city had to-- all the Jews-- had to work as [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I said, the part of the town was owned by a Pole who owned a lot of land, a lot of fields, a lot of homes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Germans took it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were working in the fields for the Germans, as forced labor, into the fields, in all kind of work that they took us every morning to go to work.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Krupp ?] was not a big town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a small town, mostly occupied from Poles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were, from before the war, certain Jews, that they lived over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But we were all subjected to [NON-ENGLISH], as soon-- as soon as the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were working in the field, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my-- my brother, my older brother and I, and my father, used to work in the field, but my mother had to tend the little baby.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But many days, she used to work in the office, over there by the Germans, or whatever they told her to do in the fields, and leave my younger brother with the baby, home.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
